<header class="entry-header">
			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.backupcentral.com/another-example-of-why-we-do-backups/" title="Permalink to Another example of why we do backups" rel="bookmark">Another example of why we do backups</a></h1>
	
		<div class="entry-meta">
		Posted on <a href="http://www.backupcentral.com/another-example-of-why-we-do-backups/" title="6:52 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2018-02-20T06:52:18+00:00" pubdate>February 20, 2018</time></a><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.backupcentral.com/author/admin/" title="View all posts by W. Curtis Preston" rel="author">W. Curtis Preston</a></span></span>	</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->	
				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>There&#8217;s a <a href="https://www.theregister.co.uk/2018/02/16/apple_file_system_bug/">story going around</a> about Apple&#8217;s MacOS APFS sparse disk images occasionally losing their mind and throwing documents out the window.  Yet another example of why we do backups.</p>
<p><img data-attachment-id="604" data-permalink="http://www.backupcentral.com/another-example-of-why-we-do-backups/shutterstock_540834766/#main" data-orig-file="https://i1.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?fit=1000%2C667" data-orig-size="1000,667" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="disk drives" data-image-description data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?fit=300%2C200" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?fit=620%2C414" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-604" src="http://www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/plugins/jetpack/modules/lazy-images/images/1x1.trans.gif" alt width="300" height="200" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i2.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?resize=300%2C200" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?resize=300%2C200 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?resize=768%2C512 768w, https://i1.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?resize=660%2C440 660w, https://i1.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?resize=240%2C160 240w, https://i2.wp.com/www.backupcentral.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/shutterstock_540834766.jpg?w=1000 1000w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 30